Name: Z.Z.Index: (6289 genres)
Notes:

  • ⎀ indicates that the genre was assigned to this collection, not by name, but by its main musical Influence.
  • Genres at top of table are more electronic and become more acoustic as you go further down the table.
Spotify playlist types:
  1. Spotify Playlist: A playlist containing a large number of songs of the given genre.
  2. Spotify Intro: An algorithmic introduction to the genre based on math and listening data from the Large Genre Collider.
  3. Spotify Pulse: The music that serious genre listeners play when they play this genre.
  4. Spotify Edge: Emerging mostly-unknown music that serious genre listeners have discovered.
